DoorType, WindowType
public abstract class _OpeningType
extends _CityObjectType

Type for openings (doors, windows) in walls. Used in LoD3 and LoD4 only. As subclass of _CityObject, an _Opening inherits all attributes and relations, in particular an id, names, external references, generic attributes and generalization relations.
